    "Name": "Mjolnir",
    "Details": "The Mjolnir B2's most obvious feature is the mace carried in the 'Mech's left hand. Based on the hatchet originally used by the Hatchetman, the mace combines with the TSM to inflict considerable damage during hand-to-hand combat. To provide covering fire, the Mjolnir uses a torso mounted ER medium laser, while an ER small laser in the right arm allows the Mjolnir to threaten battle armored infantry.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
